NAME
    Catalyst::Plugin::EmailValid - Email::Valid for Catalyst

SYNOPSIS
        use Catalyst /EmailValid/;
        ...
        $c->check_email();
    
DESCRIPTION
    This module determines whether an email address is well-formed.

  METHOD
   check_email
SEE ALSO
    Catalyst, Email::Valid

